name: ADIDAS Men Snova Glide Sports Shoes
description:
RIGID BUILD FOR CLASSIC RUNS

Though for a cushioning shoe it's quite chunky, the adidas Supernova Glide 3 gives runners that absolutely cushy heel and secure upper feel making it a widely loved running and training shoe for those with a neutral gait. Even mild overpronaTPRs find great comfort and stability in the adidas Supernova Glide 3 as it has a plushed out midsole that provides enough support. Such a construction of this shoe that weighs about 349 grams, makes it a highly recommended one for runners with mid to high arches and for those who are looking for the mild extra support.

Specially designed for the runner demanding excessive cushioning and stability, the Adidas Supernova Glide 3 is an innovative creation of an all-round shoe. A neutral trainer packed with a cushioning punch, this shoe features the AdiPRENE technology in its heel and forefoot region, providing ample cushioning both, during heelstrike and toe-off. Its rigid build encourages heel to toe transition, making it a great hit among runners with high arches. As a bonanza, the thee stripe midfoot overlay wrap and beefy midsole on the inside of the shoe add that extra support for mild overpronaTPRs.

Safe heels

While there are several neutral trainers available in the market, what sets the Adidas Supernova Glide 3 apart is that it doesn't compromise on technological features and details. Incorporating every bit of comfort that a shoe can offer you, the Adidas Supernova Glide 3 has an anti-microbial sockliner that ensures your feet are well protected from sweat and infections even during heavy workouts and long runs. Engineered with Geofit technology in the heel and collar regions for enhanced comfort and protection from impact, the Adidas Supernova Glide 3 has a soft, non-piling lining. The heel collar cup wraps around the heel for a snug and secure Fit, providing a great starting point for every stride. Such snug fit and comfort lining adapt to every stride of your foot, creating a customized feel.

Splay your toes

The meshed upper provides ample ventilation for the feet, while the three strips of reinforced synthetic leather overlays enhance midfoot support, besides representing Adidas' belief of perseverance and strength. The toe box provides ample room for your toes to spread apart comfortably when running, preventing them from brushing against the inner walls of the shoe and getting blistered. The Adidas Supernova Glide 3 also features microsuede inserts on the upper that are seamlessly stitched, providing additional structure. The lace-up system comes as an advantage adding to the snug, comfort fit and locking the foot in place.

The outsole is features a FORMOTION heel unit ensuring cushioning at its best and offering absolute comfort and tractional stability for a controlled running experience even during long runs. Created of durable rubber with AdiWEAR technology, the outsole is sure to stay your friend for years on and, even with regular use.

So jet set, get yourself an Adidas Supernova Glide 3 and sync your training goals with the absolute in cushioning, stability and style. Pair this with miCoach compatibles and track your performance, while you enjoy those long, healthy runs in these comfy, durable trainers.

Upper
White mesh uppers provide maximum ventilation
Synthetic black lace-ups for better fit
Iconic three stripes symbolising elegance and durability in silver on the sides
Padded collar and tongue, soft fabric shoe lining and cushioned insole provide all day comfort
Dual-layer adiLITE/respoEVA sockliner promotes great step-in comfort and offers anti-microbial properties
GEOFIT construction enhances comfort

Midsole
FORMOTION midsole helps to stabilize the foot and provides exceptional ground adaptability
Shock-absorbing lightweight Phylon midsole for added comfort

Outsole
Rubber toe box and heel counter for added protection
Durable outsole with horizontal pattern provides high traction
adiPRENE+ delivers supreme forefoot cushioning
adiPRENE offers under heel impact protection
TPRSION system helps to retain mid foot integrity
adiWEAR outsole supplies optimal durability in high-wear areas

Wash care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, damp cloth
Do not machine wash

If running is what your little one likes, then there's no better way to hone the skills of those young legs than with this pair of adiSPEED+ running shoes. Light in weight and well cushioned, kids are sure to find their energy doubling with each stride.

Upper
Meshed upper for maximum breathability
Strategically placed synthetic overlays for added shoe structure
Slip-on style with elastic bands on the forefoot length and a midfoot strap with a velcro closure to offer a snug, customised Fit
Meshed and padded tongue and collar for all-day comfort
Padded Ortholite footbed for in-step and anti-bacterial comfort
adidas Patented 3-Stripes on the midfoot for enhanced shoe structure and style

Midsole
Phylon insole for anabsolutely cushioned ride, lightweight comfort and enhanced impact protection

Outsole
Non-marking rubber outsole for enhanced durability, with flex grooves for ease of movement
Herringbone-styled lugs in the forefoot, with multi-directional lugs and grooves in the heel for absolute grip and traction
Scooped heel for enhanced cushioning to the backfoot and ankles

Shoe care
Wipe surface with a damp, clean cloth to remove dust and dirt
Do not wash or store in direct sunlight

name: ASICS Men Gel DS Sky Speed 2 Running Blue Sports Shoes
description:
Once you go under 10 ounces in a running shoe you have to give something up. For most shoes, it is stability. For some shoes, you lose cushioning. The asics GEL-DS Sky Speed 2 manages to retain enough of both to make this a viable everyday shoe from a category usually reserved for race day and speed work. For runners, this is an interesting buy. For long distance triathletes, it’s a secret weapon. asics has it all right with the GEL-DS Sky Speed 2, for it provides enough cushioning and stability to do Ironman distance races, coupled with absolute lightweight comfort.

Upper
Open mesh upper for supreme breathability
Synthetic leather overlays for durable, lightweight support and enhanced shoe structure
Biomorphic Fit created with a stretch material that is strategically placed throughout the upper to reduce buckling and provide an exceptional fit and feel
Asymmetrical lacing design minimizes likelihood of irritation and heightens comfort and fit
Discrete independently placed eyelets to evenly distribute lace tension for an enhanced fit
3M reflective elements allow visibility even in low light conditions
ComforDry sockliner offers anti-microbial properties for a drier, healthier environment

Midsole
Rearfoot and forefoot Gel cushioning systems work together to better attenuate impacting shock and allow fluidity of the foot throughout the gait cycle
Space Trusstic System midfoot stabilizer creates a pocket between the Trusstic System unit and the midsole, promoting more controlled midsole deformation, as well as more efficient foot function

Outsole
IGS (Impact Guidance System) to enhance the foot's natural gait from heel-strike through toe-off
Vertical flex groove that decouples the tooling along the line of progression for maximum stride efficiency
AHAR (ASICS High Abrasion Rubber) blown heel plug for excellent durability in this high-wear area

Shoe care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, cloth or brush, cold water and mild detergent to remove dust
Do not machine wash or use a drier
Avoid storing shoes in extremely hot conditions or in direct sunlight

name: ASICS Men GT 2160 Running Blue Sports Shoes
description:
GREET YOUR FEET WITH GREAT RUNS
If you are a mild to moderate overpronator looking for a daily running shoe, here's the best bet brought to you by asics. Renowned for its Fit, balanced  and cushioned ride and smooth heel to toe transition, the updated version of the asics GT 2000, the Asics GT 2160 makes you enjoy the best performance everytime. The shoe has an increased memory foam along the heel collar and forefoot, ensuring that the Asics GT 2160 offers plush cushioning and excellent shock absorption.

With stability coming as an award-winning heritage factor, the Asics GT 2160 stability running shoe has overcome those few weaknesses found in the 2150 version, making it a pleasure to run in. Reverting to the Asics GT 2140's close fit, the toe box is also narrower compared to the GT 2150, preventing the foot from shifting around in the shoe.  

Narrow or broad, take your pick
This update of the Spring 2011 running collection, the GT 2160 is the lightest running shoe of the GT 2100 series. With the lightweight feature of the GT series still intact, the GT 2160 men's shoe has increased by only 1 oz to 11.5 oz, and the women's shoe stands the same at 9.6 oz. However, unlike its predecessors, the GT 2160 doesn't have an asymmetrical lacing system, but the good old straight lacing system to provide a snug fit, locking the foot in place.

The Asics GT 2160 works wonders for those who have a narrow heel as this range of asics shoes comes with narrow sizing options. Highly recommended for overpronators, the Asics GT 2160 running shoe has an improved and more responsive cushioning that greatly contributes towards making it a long term running partner.

Torsion stability with midfoot support
The GT 2160 is employed with the Duo Max stability system, which is a harder piece of foam injected into the midsole mould, especially around the medial (inside) area of the foot, extending from below the ankle to the mid-heel, making it an ideal shoe for overpronators. This medial support can easily be recognized by its standardised grey colour that prevents the arch from collapsing excessively when running. This running shoe is also employed with the Asics Space Trusstic System stability feature that enhances midfoot support.  

On the outsole, this midfoot support is represented by a thermal plastic unit or TPU bridge that wraps around the midsole right under the inner arch of the foot, offering torsional stability. This helps prevent the foot from rotating unnaturally. However, the Trusstic System in the GT 2160 is different in men's and women's shoes, with the women's shoe having amore extended bridge that wraps the foot higher enhancing stability, as women has a wider Q-angle.

Decoupled heel for plush rides
For that extra cushioning, two units of the Asics Gel cushioning system is employed in the heel and forefoot of the Asics GT 2160. The forefoot is made much more plush, while the decoupled heel absorbs shock according to the manner in which the foot lands on the ground, distributing the impact evenly and cushioning the feet from injuries. The main change in the outsole of the Asics 2160 is that it has an Impact Guidance System (IGS). The IGS is a longitudinal groove carved in the midsole. This groove guides the foot through the most efficient stride and also reduces the weight of the shoe, enhancing running speed.

Great mileage for great runners
Constructed with synthetic overlays, the upper of the GT 2160 wraps tightly around keeping the foot locked down in place. It is employed with a rich and removable sockliner that allows the runner to fit an orthotic into the shoe for added ergonomic comfort. The ComforDry sockliner of the Asics GT 2160 provides extra amortization and anti-microbial technology that reduces bad odour and keeps the feet fresh and dry. The heel collar of the GT 2160 includes memory foam on the inside and outside, making it all the more plush and comfortable.

One of the best running shoes ever created this season, the GT 2160 is a great wear for mild to moderate overpronators. Offering plenty of support and great mileage, the Asics GT 2160 is a great buy for serious runners.

Wash care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, cloth or brush, cold water and mild detergent to remove dust
Do not machine wash or use a drier
Avoid storing shoes in extremely hot conditions or in sunlight

name: ASICS Women Gel Pulse 3 Running Black Sports Shoes
description:
FIRM Fit FOR SMOOTH RIDES

The asics Gel Pulse 3 doesn't feature is a lot of fancy padding and exotic material like its predecessor the Gel Nimbus 12. But what it does have is absolute balance. With a  cushioning that is firm enough to protect the legs during long runs, but equally soft for a comfortable ride, the just about 12 oz heavy asics Gel Pulse 3 is a highly recommended everyday trainer for runners with normal to high arches.  

With a not so ideal mushy cushioning, the forefoot of the Asics Gel Pulse 3 is designed to feel a little stiffer compared to other running shoes. This is a deliberate feature to speed up the forefoot's transition from mid-distance to toe-off.

Firm and responsive run

To add to this excellent transition are the flex grooves in the outsole that make for superb heel to toe transition, what with the Asics Gel Pulse 2 not having a very wide toe box. Engineered with this improved forefoot feel, the Asics Gel Pulse 2 is tuned towards a firm and responsive run.

Pulsing with protection and comfort

Constructed with a lightweight, breathable mesh upper, the Asics Gel Pulse 3 running shoe ensures it offers ample ventilation to the feet, keeping them dry, fresh and free of sweat. Engineered with a rearfoot Gel cushioning system, the heel is well locked in place and is protected from impact, allowing for a smooth mid-distance transition. The insole is also built with a Comforter Sockliner that not only provides ample cushioning, enhancing performance, but also employs anti-microbial properties, creating a cooler, drier and healthier environment inside the shoe.

The SpEVA midsole material improves the bounce back characteristics of the Asics Gel Pulse 3 running shoe, decreasing midsole breakdown, while the Trusstic System employed in the outsole enhances traction. This plastic shank connecting the forefoot and heel of the outsole doesn't touch the ground. It instead curves around the medial side of the foot, arching neatly and locking the foot in place.

Wash care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, cloth or brush, cold water and mild detergent to remove dust
Do not machine wash or use a drier
Avoid storing shoes in extremely hot conditions or in sunlight

name: Inc 5 Women Casual Gold Heels
description:
It's femininity celebrated and enhanced with this pair of slippers from Inc. 5. With it's sleek design and simple style, this pair looks great when paired with ethnic clothes.

This pair comes with a shoe bag that helps you carry it around in ease.

Heel: 1"

Upper
Ergonomically curved synthetic leather footbed with a padding below the heel for absolute comfort and style
Synthetic leather straps with a toe separator to hold the foot in place
Bead embellishments on the straps for ultimate style

Outsole
Durable textured and grooved rubber outsole in the forehoot and heel base for ultimate grip even on smooth surfaces

Sandal care
Wipe surface with a damp, clean cloth to remove dust and dirt
Do not wash or store in direct sunlight
